Titolo: Lands of Lore: Guardians of Destiny

Anno: 1997

Descrizione: Lands of Lore: Guardians of Destiny is a 1997 action role-playing game, second installment of the Lands of Lore series, a sequel to Lands of Lore: The Throne of Chaos. It brought about a drastic change in gameplay style from its predecessor, opting away from the original's D&D turn-based style in favor of more action elements. A sequel, Lands of Lore III, was released in 1999.

Genere: Role-playing 

Valutazione: N/A
